00:01.250 --> 00:02.310
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "QUEEN SUGAR"...</i>

00:02.350 --> 00:03.850
I THINK YOU'RE TWO MINUTES
AWAY FROM RELAPSING,

00:03.880 --> 00:05.150
AND YOU'RE NOT DOING
ANYTHING ABOUT IT.

00:05.180 --> 00:06.220
WHAT?

00:06.250 --> 00:08.290
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
YOU CALLED YOUR SPONSOR?

00:08.320 --> 00:10.890
I CAN'T GET THE IMAGE
OF YOU BEATIN' HIM

00:10.920 --> 00:12.390
OUT OF MY HEAD.

00:12.430 --> 00:13.690
I SCARED YOU.

00:13.730 --> 00:16.660
Charley: WHY DID YOU SAY
ALL THOSE THINGS?

00:16.700 --> 00:18.930
I THOUGHT I WAS DOING
SOMETHING GOOD FOR ALL OF US.

00:18.960 --> 00:21.670
BUT I SEE THAT IT WAS
JUST GOOD FOR ME.

00:21.700 --> 00:23.970
Prosper: WE SHARE THE PAIN
IT TAKES TO MOVE FORWARD.

00:24.000 --> 00:26.870
RIGHT NOW
IS WHERE WE HOLD THE LINE...

00:26.910 --> 00:29.470
WHERE WE SAY "ENOUGH,"

00:29.510 --> 00:30.840
♪ LIKE MY FIRST KISS ♪

00:30.880 --> 00:32.110
Y'ALL GOOD?

00:32.140 --> 00:33.980
♪ AND I'VE PLAYED THAT SCENE
INSIDE MY HEAD ♪

00:34.010 --> 00:35.550
♪ A THOUSAND TIMES BEFORE ♪

00:35.580 --> 00:36.810
SEE YOU TOMORROW, BABY.

00:36.850 --> 00:39.850
♪ I OPENED UP MY DOOR TO FIND ♪

00:39.890 --> 00:42.450
NOVA BORDELON,
YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED TO BE HERE.

00:42.490 --> 00:43.920
I KNOW, BUT --
SO I DON'T NEED

00:43.960 --> 00:47.730
YOU SQUATTING IN MY BOOTH
ALL MORNING LIKE A SAD PUPPY.

00:47.760 --> 00:48.990
YOU WOULDN'T GIVE ME
THE TIME OF DAY

00:49.030 --> 00:51.630
WHEN I STOPPED BY THE HOUSE,
SO I'M HERE.

00:51.660 --> 00:54.000
I WOULD REALLY LIKE
FOR US TO TALK.

00:54.030 --> 00:56.970
I MEAN NO DISRESPECT,
BUT IT'S BEEN MONTHS,

00:57.000 --> 01:00.770
AND WE'RE STILL FAMILY,
NO MATTER WHAT.

01:00.810 --> 01:04.410
I'M NOT GIVING UP.

01:04.440 --> 01:06.180
PLEASE DON'T GIVE UP ON ME.

01:06.210 --> 01:08.510
♪♪

01:08.550 --> 01:11.420
NOVA,

01:11.450 --> 01:15.090
I GOT MEMORIES
THAT I'D LEFT IN THE PAST

01:15.120 --> 01:19.390
SEEPING INTO MY BONES AGAIN,

01:19.430 --> 01:24.230
INVADING MY MIND,
MY MARRIAGE.

01:24.260 --> 01:27.730
IT DON'T FEEL GOOD.

01:27.770 --> 01:29.670
THAT'S ON YOU.

01:29.700 --> 01:31.030
YOU'RE RIGHT.

01:31.070 --> 01:35.540
I'M MORE SORRY THAN
I EVER BEEN ABOUT ANYTHING.

01:35.570 --> 01:39.110
I SHOULD HAVE DISCUSSED
WHAT I WAS DOING WITH YOU,

01:39.150 --> 01:43.010
WITH EVERYONE,
GOT YOUR BLESSING.

01:43.050 --> 01:46.150
AND IF I HAD SAID
"NO, DON'T DO IT,"

01:46.190 --> 01:49.050
WOULD YOU HAVE LISTENED?

