♪♪

15:52.430 --> 15:57.070
♪ I LONG FOR YOU ♪

15:57.100 --> 16:00.370
♪ ALL THE GOOD I'VE KNOWN ♪

16:00.410 --> 16:05.580
♪ HAS TURNED TO SORROW ♪

16:05.610 --> 16:09.250
♪ WASTE AWAY THE DAY, AFRAID ♪

16:09.280 --> 16:15.650
♪ I'VE FALLEN TOO FAR ♪

16:15.690 --> 16:21.620
♪♪

16:21.660 --> 16:25.930
♪ EASE MY SADNESS ♪

16:25.960 --> 16:28.060
[ EXHALES SHAKILY ]

16:28.100 --> 16:31.700
♪ EASE MY SORROW ♪

