♪♪

16:34.340 --> 16:38.410
♪ EASE MY SADNESS ♪

16:38.440 --> 16:41.810
♪♪

16:41.850 --> 16:42.910
Micah:
HOW'S THAT LEMONADE?

16:42.950 --> 16:45.350
THIS LEMONADE
IS KILLIN' IT.

16:45.380 --> 16:47.480
IT'S KILLIN' IT.

16:47.520 --> 16:49.250
♪♪

16:49.290 --> 16:52.190
YOU KNOW, I GOTTA GO.

16:52.220 --> 16:53.760
ALRIGHT.

16:53.790 --> 16:55.290
UH, I'LL GO WITH YOU.

16:55.330 --> 16:58.390
I CAN GO BY MYSELF.
I'M BIG.

16:58.430 --> 17:02.330
YOU SURE?
I AM SURE.

17:02.370 --> 17:03.730
ALRIGHT.

17:03.770 --> 17:09.810
♪♪

17:09.840 --> 17:15.880
♪♪

17:15.910 --> 17:17.680
OH!

17:17.720 --> 17:24.850
♪♪

17:24.890 --> 17:32.030
♪♪

17:32.060 --> 17:35.200
BLUE?

17:35.230 --> 17:36.800
BLUE!

17:36.840 --> 17:41.270
♪♪

17:41.310 --> 17:42.410
HAVE YOU GUYS SEEN A KID,

17:42.440 --> 17:43.470
UH, COME IN HERE?
NO.

17:43.510 --> 17:44.610
HE'S LIKE THIS TALL.

17:44.640 --> 17:45.880
NO, SORRY.
I MEAN, HE WAS JUST OVER HERE.

17:45.910 --> 17:47.110
HE HAS, LIKE,
A-A-A BLUE SHIRT.

17:47.150 --> 17:48.980
I-IT HAS, LIKE,
A-A SHARK ON IT.

17:49.010 --> 17:52.820
-NO. I HAVEN'T SEEN HIM.
-SORRY, MY FRIEND. NO.

17:52.850 --> 17:54.780
BLUE! BLUE!

17:54.820 --> 18:02.390
♪♪

18:02.430 --> 18:09.530
♪♪

18:09.570 --> 18:11.000
HEY, LITTLE MAN.

18:11.040 --> 18:13.170
ARE YOU LOST?

18:13.200 --> 18:15.100
I-I LOST MY COUSIN.
OH.

18:15.140 --> 18:18.140
I HAD TO GO REALLY BAD,
AND HE WAS NOT THERE.

18:18.180 --> 18:19.480
IT HAPPENS ALL THE TIME.

18:19.510 --> 18:22.080
YOU CAN COME WAIT WITH ME
WHILE HE COMES TO GET YOU, OKAY?

18:22.110 --> 18:23.850
YEAH.
LET'S GO.

18:23.880 --> 18:25.350
♪♪

18:25.380 --> 18:27.880
GOT A 920-"F"
WAITING AT STATION "C."

18:27.920 --> 18:29.220
WOMAN:
Copy that. Stand by.

18:29.250 --> 18:31.320
STEP ON IN.

18:31.360 --> 18:35.660
♪♪

18:35.690 --> 18:38.130
HEY, HE'LL FIND YOU.

18:38.160 --> 18:42.570
♪♪

18:42.600 --> 18:44.800
SYNC?
I DON'T WANT TO DO THAT.

18:44.840 --> 18:47.370
♪♪

18:47.410 --> 18:50.070
WHERE'S THE HOME BUTTON?

18:50.110 --> 18:53.380
I CAN'T SEE ANYTHING
ON THIS ITTY-BITTY SCREEN.

18:53.410 --> 18:55.210
NEED SOME HELP,
MS. VIOLET?

18:55.250 --> 18:57.050
I'M PRETTY GOOD WITH STUFF
LIKE THIS.

18:57.080 --> 18:58.650
I DON'T NEED HELP.

18:58.680 --> 19:03.920
♪♪

19:03.960 --> 19:07.120
OKAY, FINE.

19:07.160 --> 19:09.760
OKAY.
WHAT DID YOU WANT TO DO?

19:09.790 --> 19:12.630
I WANT TO KNOW HOW MANY STEPS
I HAVE SO FAR.

19:12.660 --> 19:15.300
♪♪

19:15.330 --> 19:17.600
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT,
SLOW DOWN.

19:17.640 --> 19:19.600
JUST HIT
THIS BUTTON THERE.

19:19.640 --> 19:21.300
♪♪

19:21.340 --> 19:23.940
OH, OKAY.

19:23.980 --> 19:27.810
YOU KNOW THAT YOU CAN ALSO
CHECK YOUR E-MAIL ON THAT, TOO?

19:27.850 --> 19:30.780
WHY ON EARTH WOULD I WANT
TO DO THAT?

19:30.820 --> 19:33.880
I WILL JUST
STICK TO THE BASICS.

19:33.920 --> 19:36.120
THANK YOU.

19:36.150 --> 19:38.860
NO PROBLEM.

19:38.890 --> 19:40.960
ALRIGHT.

19:40.990 --> 19:43.490
KEYS, THIS...

19:43.530 --> 19:52.940
♪♪

19:52.970 --> 19:54.540
BLUE!
Cop: HEY!

19:54.570 --> 19:55.810
THAT'S MY COUSIN.
BACK UP, ALRIGHT?

19:55.840 --> 19:57.040
NO, NO, NO.
JUST STAND BACK, ALRIGHT?

19:57.080 --> 19:58.270
THAT'S MY COUSIN
IN THE CAR.

19:58.310 --> 19:59.440
ALRIGHT, LET ME
JUST SEE SOME I.D.

19:59.480 --> 20:00.840
WHAT DO YOU NEED
TO SEE MY I.D. FOR?

20:00.880 --> 20:02.710
THAT'S MY COUSIN!
I WANT TO SEE YOUR I.D.

20:02.750 --> 20:04.850
SHOW ME YOUR I.D.
HAVE I COMMITTED A CRIME?

20:04.880 --> 20:06.420
I ASKED YOU DO SOMETHING.

20:06.450 --> 20:08.420
I EXPECT YOU TO DO IT.
DON'T PUT YOUR HANDS ON ME.

20:08.450 --> 20:10.450
I DIDN'T TOUCH YOU --
NO NEED FOR HOSTILITY, OKAY?

20:10.490 --> 20:12.090
JUST SHOW ME YOUR ID.
I DON'T NEED TO DO THAT!

20:12.120 --> 20:13.920
LET HIM OUT OF THE --
HEY! HEY! ALRIGHT.

20:13.960 --> 20:15.020
GET YOUR HANDS UP. COME ON.
WHAT --

20:15.060 --> 20:18.230
GET YOUR HANDS UP.

20:18.260 --> 20:20.100
I NEED YOU TO BE CALM.

20:20.130 --> 20:22.800
BLUE. BLUE, EVERYTHING'S
GONNA BE ALRIGHT, OKAY?

20:22.830 --> 20:25.970
♪♪

20:26.000 --> 20:27.340
BLUE, DO YOU KNOW
THIS YOUNG MAN?

20:27.370 --> 20:30.040
THAT'S MY COUSIN, MICAH.

20:30.070 --> 20:32.880
♪♪

20:32.910 --> 20:36.750
ALRIGHT, YOU STAY HERE.

20:36.780 --> 20:38.350
OKAY, KIDDO.

20:38.380 --> 20:42.690
♪♪

20:42.720 --> 20:44.620
YOU OKAY?

20:44.660 --> 20:46.390
YOU SURE?

20:53.500 --> 20:56.330
[ SIGHS ]
WHERE'S THE GUY --

20:56.370 --> 20:57.930
DARLA?

20:57.970 --> 21:01.100
♪♪

21:01.140 --> 21:02.370
YOU OKAY?

21:02.410 --> 21:04.340
YEAH, I'M JUST, UM --

21:04.380 --> 21:06.840
JUST LOOKING FOR BLUE.

21:06.880 --> 21:09.980
MICAH, UM, BROUGHT HIM
TO THE PARK.

21:10.010 --> 21:11.650
WELL, THEY'RE NOT HERE.

21:11.680 --> 21:13.450
THEY AT CITY PARK
OVER IN NEW ORLEANS.

21:13.480 --> 21:14.880
OH, RIGHT.

21:14.920 --> 21:15.920
SHIT.

21:15.950 --> 21:18.690
SORRY.

21:18.720 --> 21:21.220
SORRY.

21:21.260 --> 21:23.290
WHAT YOU BEEN DOING TODAY,
DARLA?

21:23.330 --> 21:24.860
I'M JUST, UM --

21:24.900 --> 21:27.160
I NEED TO, UM, FIND BLUE.

21:27.200 --> 21:30.000
I NEED TO FIND MY SON.

21:30.030 --> 21:31.070
OKAY.

21:31.100 --> 21:32.800
COME ON.
LET ME TAKE YOU HOME.

21:32.840 --> 21:34.540
COME ON.
NO, I NEED TO, UM --

21:34.570 --> 21:36.110
IT'S OKAY, BABY.
I'M NOT GONNA HURT YOU.

21:36.140 --> 21:38.610
I DON'T NEED YOU
TO TAKE ME HOME.

21:38.640 --> 21:40.610
OKAY, I TELL YOU WHAT.
LET'S GO FIND BLUE.

21:40.650 --> 21:41.780
LET'S GO FIND BLUE, BABY.

21:41.810 --> 21:43.380
NO.
COME ON.

21:43.410 --> 21:44.410
COME ON.
I'M FINE. I'M FINE!

21:44.450 --> 21:45.510
ALRIGHT.
LET'S GO FIND BLUE.

21:45.550 --> 21:46.680
OKAY, BUT...
OKAY?

21:46.720 --> 21:48.120
...I CAN WALK.

21:48.150 --> 21:49.520
ALRIGHT?
I CAN WALK!

21:49.550 --> 21:52.620
ALRIGHT.
OKAY.

21:52.660 --> 21:54.190
ALRIGHT.

21:54.230 --> 21:57.490
I SEE YOU AND MS. GENEVIEVE
BEEN LOOKING REAL COZY NOWADAYS,

21:57.530 --> 21:59.800
-MR. PROSPER, UH-HUH.
-[ CHUCKLES ]

21:59.830 --> 22:02.430
LOOK, I MAY OR MAY NOT
HAVE SEEN Y'ALL EVERY DAY

22:02.470 --> 22:03.930
-IN A CERTAIN BOOTH...
-MM-HMM.

22:03.970 --> 22:05.630
...AT A CERTAIN
PIE ESTABLISHMENT...

22:05.670 --> 22:07.540
-MM.
-...IN THIS HERE FINE TOWN.

22:07.570 --> 22:08.900
[ LAUGHTER ]

22:08.940 --> 22:10.240
MAY OR MAY NOT HAVE.
I DON'T KNOW.

22:10.270 --> 22:11.540
MAY OR MAY NOT HAVE.

22:11.580 --> 22:13.310
[ LAUGHTER ]

22:13.340 --> 22:15.140
YEAH, WELL, I TELL YOU,

22:15.180 --> 22:18.110
IT'S NICE TO KEEP COMPANY
WITH SOMEBODY.

22:18.150 --> 22:19.250
-MM-HMM.
-MM.

22:19.280 --> 22:21.380
YOU KNOW, AND SHE'S A --
SHE'S A GOOD WOMAN.

22:21.420 --> 22:23.590
-SHE GOT A KIND HEART.
-MM-HMM.

22:23.620 --> 22:27.020
AND I ADMIT THAT
I'M KIND OF SWEET ON HER.

22:27.060 --> 22:29.290
WHOO! SURE ENOUGH!
AHH, THAT'S WHAT I LIKE TO HEAR,

22:29.330 --> 22:31.390
-MR. PROSPER.
-SURE YOU'RE RIGHT.

22:31.430 --> 22:33.230
THAT'S SOME GOOD NEWS
RIGHT THERE.

22:33.260 --> 22:35.360
YEAH, NO,
IT'S MIGHTY NICE. YEAH.

22:35.400 --> 22:37.200
IT SEEM LIKE WE'RE ALL DOING
PRETTY GOOD

22:37.240 --> 22:40.000
IN THE LOVE DEPARTMENT
THESE DAYS.

22:40.040 --> 22:41.500
-MM.
-I MEAN, YOU KNOW.

22:41.540 --> 22:43.170
VI'S THE BEST WOMAN
IN TOWN.

22:43.210 --> 22:44.510
YEAH, SHE IS.

22:44.540 --> 22:48.380
AND SPEAKING OF BOOTHS
AT FINE PIE ESTABLISHMENTS...

22:48.410 --> 22:50.310
[ CHUCKLES ]
...I'VE SEEN YOU

22:50.350 --> 22:52.550
AND THAT PRETTY LADY LAWYER.

22:52.580 --> 22:54.480
YEAH, SHE REAL COOL.

22:54.520 --> 22:55.750
LIKE HER A LOT.

22:55.790 --> 22:57.190
MM.

22:57.220 --> 23:00.520
FEEL LIKE SHE SEE ME --
THE GOOD, THE BAD.

23:00.560 --> 23:03.030
-MM.
-WON'T TAKE THAT FOR GRANTED.

23:03.060 --> 23:05.360
Y'ALL GETTING SERIOUS, HUH?

23:05.400 --> 23:07.160
SERIOUS ENOUGH, I GUESS.

23:07.200 --> 23:08.830
GOT A LITTLE DATE TONIGHT.

23:08.870 --> 23:11.900
TALK TO HER ABOUT
TAKING THINGS UP A NOTCH...

23:11.940 --> 23:13.200
MM!

23:13.240 --> 23:14.940
...MAKING IT EXCLUSIVE.

23:14.970 --> 23:16.840
SEE HOW SHE FEEL ABOUT IT.

23:16.870 --> 23:19.480
RALPH ANGEL GONNA HAVE
A WHOLE GIRLFRIEND!

23:19.510 --> 23:20.510
I AIN'T MAD AT YOU.

23:20.550 --> 23:22.410
A WHOLE ONE?

23:22.450 --> 23:23.610
AND A HALF.

23:23.650 --> 23:26.880
HEY!
[ LAUGHTER ]

23:26.920 --> 23:28.550
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

23:28.590 --> 23:31.350
I DON'T THINK WE'VE SHARED
A ROOM SINCE WE WERE LITTLE

23:31.390 --> 23:34.890
AT DADDY'S --
WELL, SOMETIMES AT DADDY'S.

23:37.800 --> 23:39.500
SUMMERS.

23:41.700 --> 23:44.370
THERE WAS ANOTHER TIME.

23:44.400 --> 23:47.470
WHEN?

23:47.510 --> 23:49.710
THAT WEEKEND
I VISITED YOU IN L.A.

23:49.740 --> 23:52.340
IN '99.

23:52.380 --> 23:53.880
YOU WERE STILL
IN HIGH SCHOOL.

23:53.910 --> 23:56.510
I WAS A FRESHMAN
AT TULANE.

23:56.550 --> 23:57.750
YOUR MOM HAD A GUEST ROOM,
OF COURSE,

23:57.780 --> 24:01.020
BUT WE SAID
WE WANTED TO STAY TOGETHER.

24:01.050 --> 24:03.920
[ CHUCKLES ]
YEAH.

24:03.960 --> 24:07.660
YEP, I REMEMBER THAT.

24:07.690 --> 24:12.130
FEELS LIKE FOREVER AGO.

24:12.160 --> 24:14.200
IT<i> WAS</i> FOREVER AGO.

24:14.230 --> 24:17.200
YOU TOOK ME TO THIS PARTY.

24:17.240 --> 24:21.540
THE HOUSE WAS
THE SIZE OF SAINT JO.

24:21.570 --> 24:23.770
WE GOT THERE, AND YOU SAID,

24:23.810 --> 24:28.410
"ALL MY FRIENDS ARE HERE,
SO BE COOL.

24:28.450 --> 24:30.850
JUST ACT LIKE YOU BELONG."

24:30.880 --> 24:32.150
I DON'T REMEMBER
SAYING THAT.

24:32.180 --> 24:36.020
YOU DITCHED ME
MOST OF THE NIGHT.

24:36.050 --> 24:38.390
I WAS SO OUT OF PLACE.

24:38.420 --> 24:42.060
EVERYONE LOOKED LIKE THEY'D JUST
POPPED OUT OF A RALPH LAUREN AD.

24:42.090 --> 24:44.290
WHEN I FINALLY FOUND YOU,

24:44.330 --> 24:48.200
I OVERHEARD YOUR FRIEND ASK
IF I WAS YOUR SISTER,

24:48.230 --> 24:50.630
AND YOU SAID,

24:50.670 --> 24:53.770
"SHE'S JUST MY HALF-SISTER.

24:53.800 --> 24:56.370
SHE'S ALRIGHT,

24:56.410 --> 24:59.610
BUT YOU CAN'T
CHOOSE YOUR FAMILY."

24:59.640 --> 25:02.380
I DON'T REMEMBER
SAYING THAT.

25:02.410 --> 25:04.480
♪♪

25:04.520 --> 25:08.580
I REMEMBER BEING SO EXCITED

25:08.620 --> 25:11.690
THAT MY BIG SISTER
WAS COMING TO VISIT...

25:11.720 --> 25:14.220
♪♪

25:14.260 --> 25:18.660
AND THEN BEING DEVASTATED,
BECAUSE...

25:18.700 --> 25:21.960
YOU SPENT THE WHOLE TIME

25:22.000 --> 25:25.000
PUTTING ME DOWN,

25:25.040 --> 25:27.840
ABOUT MY HOUSE,

25:27.870 --> 25:31.710
MY CLOTHES, MY FRIENDS.

25:31.740 --> 25:36.050
YOU TOOK ME TO PLACES
YOU KNEW I COULDN'T AFFORD,

25:36.080 --> 25:38.680
OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

25:38.720 --> 25:42.750
NOVA, I WAS TREATING YOU.

25:42.790 --> 25:47.320
IT DIDN'T FEEL LIKE THAT TO ME,
AT THE TIME.

25:47.360 --> 25:50.290
♪♪

25:50.330 --> 25:55.030
FOR SOME REASON,
I ALWAYS FEEL SMALL AROUND YOU,

25:55.070 --> 25:57.530
STILL.

25:57.570 --> 25:59.840
FOR A LONG TIME,
I THOUGHT THAT WAS ON ME.

25:59.870 --> 26:01.900
♪♪

26:01.940 --> 26:06.310
AT SOME POINT, I CAME
TO FEEL IT WAS ON YOU.

26:06.340 --> 26:08.580
BUT BOTH ARE WRONG.

26:08.610 --> 26:12.920
SOMETIMES THINGS ARE JUST
THE WAY THEY ARE.

26:12.950 --> 26:19.320
♪♪

26:19.360 --> 26:25.190
♪♪

26:25.230 --> 26:31.870
EVERY TIME I THINK WE'RE --
WE'RE STARTING TO UNDERSTAND,

26:31.900 --> 26:35.170
IT'S CLEAR TO ME,
AFTER ALL THIS TIME,

26:35.210 --> 26:40.640
WE STILL DON'T KNOW EACH OTHER
AS WELL AS WE THINK WE DO.

26:40.680 --> 26:46.850
♪♪

26:46.880 --> 26:49.250
I CAN'T, UH --

26:49.290 --> 26:52.090
I JUST CAN'T --
I CAN'T REMEMBER IT.

26:52.120 --> 26:55.760
BLUE DOESN'T --
BLUE DOESN'T DESERVE THIS.

26:55.790 --> 26:58.630
OH, GOD, IT'S --

26:58.660 --> 27:01.760
IT'S ALL MY FAULT.

27:01.800 --> 27:03.530
WHAT'S YOUR FAULT, BABY?

27:03.570 --> 27:06.240
♪♪

27:06.270 --> 27:08.670
LOOK AT ME.

27:08.710 --> 27:12.810
YOU AND ME, WE GOT A PAST,

27:12.840 --> 27:16.110
BUT I KNOW YOU BEEN DOING BETTER
THAN THIS, SO WHAT HAPPENED?

27:16.150 --> 27:17.780
♪♪

27:17.820 --> 27:20.080
LET IT OUT,

27:20.120 --> 27:24.590
WHATEVER IT IS THAT MADE YOU
DO THIS TO YOURSELF.

27:24.620 --> 27:26.990
I CAN'T.

27:27.020 --> 27:29.890
I CAN'T TALK TO YOU...

27:29.930 --> 27:31.830
ABOUT THIS.

27:35.170 --> 27:38.370
YOU'RE GONNA LET THIS THING
TAKE OVER AGAIN...

27:42.010 --> 27:45.040
...DESTROY EVERYTHING
YOU'VE WORKED FOR?

28:02.060 --> 28:06.700
♪♪

28:06.730 --> 28:07.960
I --

28:08.000 --> 28:11.170
I DIDN'T --
I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT I WAS DOING.

28:11.200 --> 28:12.940
♪♪

28:12.970 --> 28:17.770
I WAS SO OUT OF IT
THAT NIGHT.

28:17.810 --> 28:21.280
♪♪

28:21.310 --> 28:23.550
[ GROANS ]

28:23.580 --> 28:25.680
♪♪

28:25.720 --> 28:28.380
GO ON, BABY.
SPEAK IT.

28:28.420 --> 28:30.890
♪♪

28:30.920 --> 28:33.090
I, UM...

28:33.120 --> 28:36.990
♪♪

28:37.030 --> 28:40.400
I FOUND --
I FOUND OUT THERE WERE

28:40.430 --> 28:43.300
TWO --

28:43.330 --> 28:46.070
TWO GUYS, BUT I DON'T --

28:46.100 --> 28:49.040
I DON'T REMEMBER
ANY OF IT.

28:49.070 --> 28:52.780
I DON'T --
BEING WITH THEM.

28:52.810 --> 28:55.410
I CAN'T FIGURE IT --

28:55.450 --> 29:03.520
♪♪

29:03.550 --> 29:08.790
NOBODY MADE SURE
YOU WAS OKAY ENOUGH

29:08.830 --> 29:10.530
TO BE INVOLVED IN ALL THAT?

29:10.560 --> 29:14.830
I WAS -- GOD,
I WAS SO MESSED UP. I --

29:14.870 --> 29:17.530
I WAS, UH --
I WAS REALLY HIGH.

29:17.570 --> 29:20.800
♪♪

29:20.840 --> 29:23.870
IT'S GONE.

29:23.910 --> 29:27.080
BUT I SHOULDN'T
HAVE BEEN THERE.

29:27.110 --> 29:29.380
GOD. OH.

29:29.410 --> 29:32.250
DARLA?

29:32.280 --> 29:34.520
BABY, YOU LISTEN TO ME.

29:34.550 --> 29:37.150
LISTEN.

29:37.190 --> 29:40.620
IF YOU ARE OUT OF IT,

29:40.660 --> 29:44.560
THEN YOU ARE NOT
IN THE RIGHT MIND

29:44.600 --> 29:48.760
TO AGREE TO ANYTHING.

29:48.800 --> 29:50.570
DO YOU HEAR ME?

29:50.600 --> 29:52.600
♪♪

29:52.640 --> 29:55.040
AND THAT AIN'T
JUST MY OPINION.

29:55.070 --> 29:56.640
THAT'S THE LAW.

29:56.670 --> 29:58.270
♪♪

29:58.310 --> 30:00.080
YOU UNDERSTAND?

30:00.110 --> 30:02.480
BUT I --
"BUT," MY ASS.

30:02.510 --> 30:04.610
THERE IS NO "BUT" HERE.

30:04.650 --> 30:08.980
♪♪

30:09.020 --> 30:12.250
I WAS --

30:12.290 --> 30:13.860
I WAS --

30:13.890 --> 30:16.730
♪♪

30:16.760 --> 30:19.930
MAYBE --

30:19.960 --> 30:22.460
MAYBE I DIDN'T SAY NO.

30:22.500 --> 30:25.930
♪♪

30:25.970 --> 30:29.270
AND MAYBE YOU DID,

30:29.310 --> 30:31.470
