YOU DIDN'T SAY NOTHING

30:31.510 --> 30:33.280
'CAUSE YOU COULDN'T.

30:33.310 --> 30:35.740
♪♪

30:35.780 --> 30:38.880
IF YOU CAN'T REMEMBER
ANY OF THIS...

30:38.920 --> 30:46.390
♪♪

30:46.420 --> 30:53.030
♪♪

30:53.060 --> 30:57.100
