THE WAY IT HAD TO BE.

31:08.380 --> 31:10.980
♪♪

31:11.020 --> 31:14.620
I EVEN STOPPED SAYING NO...

31:14.650 --> 31:17.050
♪♪

31:17.090 --> 31:18.620
...BECAUSE IT DIDN'T
SEEM TO MATTER.

31:18.660 --> 31:21.390
I BLAMED MYSELF,

31:21.430 --> 31:24.360
THOUGHT THERE WAS SOMETHING
WRONG WITH ME.

31:24.400 --> 31:27.860
♪♪

31:27.900 --> 31:31.230
BUT I KNOW NOW

31:31.270 --> 31:36.570
THAT IT WASN'T RIGHT THEN,
AND IT AIN'T RIGHT NOW.

31:36.610 --> 31:38.340
NO MEANS NO.

31:38.380 --> 31:40.010
♪♪

31:40.040 --> 31:43.680
DON'T MATTER
THE CIRCUMSTANCES.

31:43.710 --> 31:46.980
AND EVEN IF YOU --

31:47.020 --> 31:50.690
YOU DON'T SAY NO...

31:50.720 --> 31:53.890
OR CAN'T,

31:53.920 --> 31:55.990
DON'T NO MAN
OR ANYBODY ELSE

31:56.030 --> 31:59.030
