TO TAKE ADVANTAGE OF YOU.

31:59.060 --> 32:03.070
♪♪

32:03.100 --> 32:05.330
THAT'S RAPE.

32:05.370 --> 32:15.010
♪♪

32:17.400 --> 32:20.300
[ MEN LAUGHING,
SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

32:20.330 --> 32:22.800
♪♪

32:22.840 --> 32:24.370
-WHAT'S UP, BUDDY?
-HEY.

32:24.410 --> 32:26.410
