WITH YOUR BIG COUSIN?

32:26.440 --> 32:29.110
I SAT IN THE BACK
OF A POLICE CAR.

32:29.140 --> 32:32.940
POLICE CAR?

32:32.980 --> 32:34.710
WHAT?

32:34.750 --> 32:36.880
♪♪

32:36.920 --> 32:39.690
I JUST -- I LOST -- I LOST TRACK
OF HIM FOR LIKE ONE SECOND,

32:39.720 --> 32:42.420
AND -- AND THE COPS FOUND HIM.

32:42.460 --> 32:44.490
THEY WEREN'T NICE
TO HIM, POPS.

32:44.530 --> 32:53.270
♪♪

32:53.300 --> 32:55.230
YOUNG MAN, IT'S OKAY
IF YOU AIN'T OKAY.

32:55.270 --> 32:57.000
YOU KNOW THAT, RIGHT?

32:57.040 --> 33:01.670
♪♪

33:01.710 --> 33:04.380
YOU A'IGHT?

33:04.410 --> 33:07.650
I MEAN,
I'M JUST TIRED OF IT.

33:07.680 --> 33:13.850
♪♪

33:13.890 --> 33:15.250
WE CAN'T NEVER GET SO TIRED

33:15.290 --> 33:19.190
WE START LETTING OTHER FOLKS
TELL US WHO WE ARE.

33:19.230 --> 33:20.730
YOU HEAR ME?
YES, SIR.

33:20.760 --> 33:21.860
YOU KEEP YOUR HEAD UP.

33:21.900 --> 33:23.830
DON'T LET THEM PUT YOU
IN THAT PLACE,

33:23.860 --> 33:27.170
THAT DARK PLACE.

33:27.200 --> 33:31.070
YOU KEEP LIVING, LOVING,
GROWING, AND DOING FOR OTHERS.

33:31.110 --> 33:33.740
THAT'S THE KEY,
JUST LIKE WE DO FOR YOU.

33:33.770 --> 33:37.010
YOU MAKE SURE YOU DO IT
FOR SOMEBODY ELSE.

33:37.040 --> 33:39.180
YEAH.

33:39.210 --> 33:40.550
YOU HEAR?

33:40.580 --> 33:43.950
YEAH, I HEAR YOU.

33:43.980 --> 33:45.550
THANK YOU.

33:45.590 --> 33:50.460
♪♪

33:50.490 --> 33:54.560
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

33:54.600 --> 33:56.030
WHAT'S UP, AUNT VI?

33:56.060 --> 33:58.160
