to meet me at Darla's.

33:58.200 --> 34:00.500
DARLA'S?
GOT BLUE RIGHT HERE WITH ME.

34:00.530 --> 34:03.900
I NEED YOU TO MEET ME HERE
RIGHT NOW,

34:03.940 --> 34:05.540
PLEASE,

34:05.570 --> 34:08.440
alone.

34:08.480 --> 34:10.280
A'IGHT.

34:13.050 --> 34:15.380
I'M SORRY TO, UH,

34:15.420 --> 34:18.320
HAVE CALLED YOU OVER LIKE THIS,
BUT, UM...

34:21.020 --> 34:23.590
...I-I WANTED TO TALK TO YOU
BEFORE BLUE GOT HOME.

34:26.560 --> 34:28.760
