WHAT THIS ABOUT.

34:30.760 --> 34:34.430
Y'ALL JUST SITTING THERE
LIKE THAT.

34:34.470 --> 34:36.370
TRUTH IS
I'M SCARED ALREADY.

34:38.540 --> 34:41.010
THERE'S NOTHING TO BE
SCARED ABOUT.

34:41.040 --> 34:45.180
THE TRUTH IS A LIGHT,
EVEN WHEN IT DON'T FEEL LIKE IT.

34:48.950 --> 34:51.920
I, UM...

34:51.950 --> 34:56.420
I WANTED TO, UH, TALK TO YOU
ABOUT, UM...

34:59.130 --> 35:01.190
...THE NIGHT THAT BLUE
WAS CONCEIVED.

35:02.830 --> 35:05.900
I-I FOUND OUT THAT, UM --

35:08.240 --> 35:14.970
THAT THERE WERE TWO.

35:15.010 --> 35:16.680
TWO?

35:19.050 --> 35:22.410
TWO WHAT?

35:22.450 --> 35:24.150
TWO, UH...

35:27.860 --> 35:31.220
TWO GUYS

35:31.260 --> 35:33.590
THAT I WAS WITH.

35:33.630 --> 35:37.760
♪♪

35:37.800 --> 35:39.760
I DON'T REMEMBER.

35:39.800 --> 35:43.840
♪♪

35:43.870 --> 35:46.740
I, UH -- I DON'T --

35:46.770 --> 35:50.340
[ SNIFFLES, SIGHS ]

35:50.380 --> 35:54.250
I DON'T REMEMBER BECAUSE, UH,

35:54.280 --> 35:58.180
I WAS OUT OF IT,

35:58.220 --> 36:02.190
COMPLETELY.

36:02.220 --> 36:03.790
I, UH --

36:03.820 --> 36:06.690
I REALIZED, UH...

36:06.730 --> 36:09.230
FOR THE FIRST TIME THAT, UM...

36:09.260 --> 36:14.070
♪♪

36:14.100 --> 36:19.100
...I COULDN'T HAVE AGREED
TO BE WITH THEM

36:19.140 --> 36:22.240
IN THAT STATE.

36:22.280 --> 36:24.440
I, UH...

36:24.480 --> 36:26.550
♪♪

36:26.580 --> 36:28.480
I-I DIDN'T REALIZE IT BEFORE,

36:28.520 --> 36:32.050
BUT, UM,

36:32.090 --> 36:34.890
I REALIZE IT NOW.

36:34.920 --> 36:38.090
I WAS, UM...

36:38.130 --> 36:41.660
[ SIGHS SHAKILY ]

36:41.700 --> 36:44.000
I WAS, UM...

36:53.370 --> 36:55.170
I'M SORRY.

36:55.210 --> 36:59.710
♪♪

36:59.750 --> 37:01.350
NO.

37:01.380 --> 37:03.920
YOU AIN'T GOTTA BE SORRY.

37:03.950 --> 37:05.620
♪♪

37:05.650 --> 37:09.550
AIN'T GOTTA
BE SORRY, OKAY?

37:09.590 --> 37:11.920
YOU AIN'T GOTTA BE SORRY.

37:11.960 --> 37:16.130
I'M GONNA GIVE YOU BOTH
SOME TIME.

37:16.160 --> 37:17.700
AIN'T GOTTA BE SORRY.

37:17.730 --> 37:19.430
HEY.

37:19.470 --> 37:23.940
♪♪

37:23.970 --> 37:28.210
I'M SORRY FOR DRINKING,

37:28.240 --> 37:31.940
