THROUGH THIS.

37:36.450 --> 37:38.220
HEY.

37:38.250 --> 37:46.360
♪♪

37:46.390 --> 37:49.130
YOU GOT NOTHING
TO APOLOGIZE FOR.

37:49.160 --> 37:51.130
♪♪

37:51.160 --> 37:52.930
GONNA GET THROUGH IT.

37:52.970 --> 37:54.930
YOU HEAR ME?

37:54.970 --> 37:57.470
ALL YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH,

37:57.500 --> 38:00.110
