38:04.910 --> 38:06.610
HUH?

38:06.650 --> 38:08.610
WHATEVER IT TAKE, DARLA,

38:08.650 --> 38:10.920
YOU KNOW
I'M RIGHT HERE WITH YOU.

38:10.950 --> 38:12.420
YOU KNOW THAT.

38:12.450 --> 38:16.860
I'M RIGHT HERE, OKAY?

38:16.890 --> 38:20.490
MY BLUE. I'M --

38:20.530 --> 38:23.800
I'M SCARED.

38:23.830 --> 38:26.530
