38:31.370 --> 38:33.200
HEAR ME?

38:33.240 --> 38:34.840
YOU'RE GONNA BE ALRIGHT.

38:34.880 --> 38:37.610
COME HERE. COME HERE.

38:37.640 --> 38:46.020
♪♪

38:46.050 --> 38:48.590
